  <title>Gwibber lens</title>

  <p>The Gwibber lens is the third lens after the Dash home in the
    <gui>lens bar</gui> and is represented by a bird. The Gwibber lens
    gives you easy access to your online social media accounts.</p>

  <p>You can use <keyseq><key>Super</key><key>G</key></keyseq> to open the
    Dash directly at the Gwibber lens.</p>

  <item><p>The lens will be blank until you enter your credentials in 
    <link xref="accounts">Online Accounts</link>.</p></item>

<section id="dash-apps-previews">
  <title>Previews</title>

  <p>Right click on a search result to open a <gui>preview</gui>. The preview
    gives you more information and allows you to easily "like" or reshare posts.</p>

</section>

<section id="dash-apps-filters">
